results.Title: Travel Backpack 45L
results.Description: This rugged, expandable, and accessible carry-on travel backpack features top, side, front, and rear access via weatherproof UltraZips. It expands to 45L for gear hauling and collapses to 35L for daily use. With quick-access pockets, expandable side pockets, padded laptop + tablet sleeves, tuck-away shoulder straps and hip belt, 360-degree grab handles, and cleverly concealed external carry straps. It's packed in a sleek, weatherproof 100% recycled 400D nylon canvas shell with a 900D bottom liner. Fair Trade Certified and 100% carbon neutral.
